A man killed, woman and child critically injuredin a collision between two cars on the N1 north by the Maraisburg offramp on Saturday.On arrival ER24 paramedics found a man trapped in one of the vehicle. Sadly he was declared dead.ER24 Spokesperson Chitra Bodasing Harduth said &#8220;The second occupant of this vehicle sustained minor injuries.The woman and a female child believed to be about 3/4 years old travelling in the second vehicle were assessed and treated for their injuries&#8221;.The cause of the incident is unknown.-TNA Reporter 